Timestamp: Speaker 1: Abhi kaafi updates bhi ma'am humne kar rahe hain. Ma'am jaise pregnancy jo plan hai, uske andar yoga aur pregnancy...
Transcript: Abhi kaafi updates bhi ma'am humne kar rahe hain. Ma'am jaise pregnancy jo plan hai, uske andar yoga aur pregnancy. Actually usme charges zyada hai, toh patient ne register kiya bhi tha, aisa nahi hai ki nahi kiya tha, par shayad charges issue se hoga kuch. Accha ma'am abhi humne offerings bhi increase kar di hain. Ma'am jo plans hain usme hum diet, yoga, mental health ke saath hi labor management, lactation counseling, garbh sanskar, physiotherapy, web nurse karwane lag gaye hain. And ma'am yoga mein batch size bhi bahut humne kam kar diya hai. Matlab keval thirty ya fifty log hi hote hain, usse zyada log nahi hote hain. And pregnancy plans ko do parts mein humne divide kar rakha hai. Jo second se fourth month ke andar add hote hain, unhe diet, yoga, mental health support ke saath hum garbh sanskar aur physiotherapy ka abhyas karwate hain and jo fifth se eighth month mein add hote hain, unhe one-on-one birth coaching usme batate hain ki baby hone wala hai toh kaise uska pura dhyan rakhna hai, diapering kaise karna hai, matlab sab kuch unhe batate hain. Early baby care webinars bhi humne add kiya hai, lactation counseling bhi add kiya hai ma'am. Iske liye Dr. Manisha Mohan hain unhe bhi humne hire kiya tha, jinka kaafi accha experience hai CK Birla aur Fortis Bangalore ke andar, twelve plus years ka, toh wohi pure sessions ma'am karwayengi, Lamaze course aur labor management ke.

Timestamp: Speaker 1: Isme, ma'am ye jo hamare experts hain sabhi, in sabhi ka experience fifty plus years ka hai combined mein. Jaise dietician Riya hain ye thirty plus dieticians ko lead kar rahi hain. Amrita yoga instructor hain, inke bhi ten plus logon ki team hai. So overall na hum patient ko hum pura holistic care provide kar rahe hain abhi and Jaipur mein hundred plus doctors hain ma'am abhi jo use kar rahe hain kaafi ache se. And patients ke feedback aur in terms of revenue also ma'am kaafi increase ho gaya hai abhi. Ma'am Gugun ke, Gullabh ji ke ya Surya ke mostly saare doctors ma'am use kar rahe hain. Unke alawa bhi kaafi doctors ma'am hain. Toh ma'am main chahta hun ki aap bhi wo start karen wapas se.
